## Context

- **IL-23 atlas third dataset RESOLVED (#1367)**: Kong et al. Immunity 2023 (PMID 36720220) identified as IBDverse replacement. 430K terminal ileum cells (154K epithelial, 201K immune, 76K stromal), 46 CD + 25 controls. Freely downloadable from CellxGene (collection 5c868b6f, H5AD ~2GB total). Also on Broad SCP1884. Dev task #1417 created for download.
- **Kong Nat Genet 2025 (#1408/#1064)**: SCP2959 on Single Cell Portal (processed), phs003943 on dbGaP (controlled). GitHub has code + data files. Processed viewable but raw requires authorization.
- **Washburn JCC 2026 (#930)**: Data likely at SCP1422/SCP1423 (Broad). 14 pediCD + 13 FGID, 254K cells. Cell-by-gene matrices should be released with peer-reviewed version.
- **GSE282122 confirmed (#207)**: Thomas/Buckley Nat Immunol 2024 anti-TNF atlas. ~1M cells, 216 biopsies, 41 subjects. Filtered h5 files (2.8 GB) downloadable. Dev task created.
- **PRJNA1216747 (#324)**: Rabinowitz inception cohort 16S confirmed on SRA. 73 CD, 146 runs, MiSeq. Only 2 timepoints — baseline validation only, not longitudinal modeling.
- **IBDverse (#208/#448) STILL BLOCKED**: Zenodo restricted. CellxGene Kong 2023 is replacement.
- **SPARC IBD (#271/#1065) BLOCKED**: Metabolomics not publicly available. Requires formal IBD Plexus request.
- **McGregor fistula atlas (#810) BLOCKED**: dbGaP phs003943 controlled access.
- **Sci Rep 2026 paired data (#453) AVAILABLE**: PRJNA1053872 (16S), PRJNA1057679 (shotgun), supplementary metabolomics. 80 CD + 43 HC. Dev task created.
- **Pediatric multi-omics (#173) AVAILABLE**: MTBLS9877, PRJEB74164, PXD062519. 58 pediCD. Dev task created.
- **IBD inception cohort (#172)**: PRJEB86986 on ENA. 23 CD + 37 UC + 20 HC. Small CD cohort.
- **Acharjee stricture genes (#233)**: 8 key genes (LY96, AKAP11, SRM, GREM1, EHD2, SERPINE1, HDAC1, FGF2) for feature engineering. Primary data not deposited.
- **GSE16879 (#505)**: Available but lacks B1/B2/B3 behavior annotation. Not suitable for stricture validation.
- **Gudiño perianal scRNA-seq (#357)**: GEO accession not confirmed. GSE260833 is different study.
- **IBDTransDB**: abbviegrc.shinyapps.io/ibdtransdb/ confirmed. 34 datasets, SQLite downloadable.
- New dev tasks created: #1417 (CellxGene Kong download), GSE282122 download, Sci Rep 2026 data, pediatric multi-omics. Analyst task for HMP2 fatty acid amide check.
- Journal entries: #2305-2309, #2313.
